Package gw.api.diff.node

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDiffItemTreeNode<T extends IDiffTreeNode<T>>
    Represents a node backed by a DiffItem }in the policy difference tree infrastructure.
    IDiffTreeNode<T extends IDiffTreeNode<T>>
    Represents a node in the policy difference tree infrastructure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDiffItemDiffTreeNode
    A difference tree node that is based off of a DiffItem passed to its constructor.
    AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode
    An implementation of IDiffTreeNode that orders its children based on the AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode.getSortOrder() and then AbstractOrderedDiffTreeNode.getLabel() properties.
    AddDiffTreeNode
    An add row in the difference tree.
    ChangeDiffTreeNode
    A property change row in the difference tree.
    LabelDiffTreeNode
    A labeled (non-title) row in the difference tree.
    RemoveDiffTreeNode
    A remove row in the difference tree.
    TextDiffTreeNode
    A difference tree node that only contains text in the Label property (and, therefore, none in Value1 or Value2).
    TitleDiffTreeNode
    A title (or header) row in the difference tree.
